API Building : 

Customer : 
- Add or Remove item in the Cart -----------------------------------> Done
- Add or Remove item in the Wishlist -------------------------------> Done
- Order an Item ----------------------------------------------------> Done
- Cancel Ordered Item ----------------------------------------------> Done
- Cancel Transaction Done ------------------------------------------> Done
- Revert the Money Back for Cancelling Item ------------------------> Done
- Transaction for an order -----------------------------------------> Done
- Mark Transactionas Cancelled with Msg for an order ---------------> Done
- View all the items -----------------------------------------------> Done
- View Profile -----------------------------------------------------> Done {Done from auth.js}
- Update Account Balance on Ordering -------------------------------> Done
- Update Account Balance on adding or removing more money ----------> Done

